CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Rollins is a global leader in route-based pest-control services, with operations spanning North, Central and South America, Europe, the Middle East and Africa and Australia. Its portfolio of pest-control brands includes the prominent Orkin brand, market leader in the U.S.where it boasts near national coverageand in Canada. Residential pest and termite prevention predominate the services provided by Rollins, owing to the group's ongoing focus on U.S. and Canadian markets.
